<title>Messages File (.mgf)</title>

The messages file is a text file where you can store message text and an associated message number. Each line in the message file contains one message. A message consists of a message number followed by text which can be up to 240 characters long. It is displayed when an <logiccolor>errmsg</logiccolor> function with the message number is executed in a data entry application. A message may contain parameters.
